{"tid":1829318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（我冇野講）濫捕成風，重溫李安然大律師對於被捕後既應對。「我冇野講」「我要見律師」「我要去醫院」","createTime":"2020-01-18T15:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T08:06:20.000Z","uid":2383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d13744efad8e24afa960ee2fbd423930544686d1","tid":1829318,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"響BOBO 家長 「示威者」面前都要<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我冇嘢講！！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n完整版請睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KanZhongGuo.web/videos/486314495263561/?v=486314495263561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKanZhongGuo.web%2Fvideos%2F486314495263561%2F%3Fv%3D486314495263561&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1EqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=00259b76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KanZhongGuo.web/videos/486314495263561/?v=486314495263561</a> <br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">被捕後</span></strong></em><br />\n。保持冷靜<br />\n。行使緘默權-我無嘢講（唔只對BOBO，仲有家長、「示威者」）<br />\n。被捕時勿解鎖電話以致電律師及家人<br />\n。BOBO可檢取電話但你冇責任解鎖電話<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搜屋</span></strong></em><br />\n。如沒有法庭搜查令，可以講唔同意搜查屋企<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;冷靜<br />\n一定要保持冷靜，你可能會見到冇諗過嘅事會發生於你眼前，可能會見到有人被打，可能會見到律師，請一定要冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;我無嘢講<br />\n你絕對有權利行使緘默權！包括身邊陪同你的家長、一起被捕嘅「示威者」都要我無嘢講。於一件案件中，無需任何人證物證，一旦你於證供中承認你犯罪，即使這份證供是唯一證據，都足以令你定罪。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;切勿解鎖你嘅電話<br />\n記住你被捕當刻，唔好攞電話出嚟，唔好打電話比你嘅律師/屋企人，因為你攞電話出嚟解鎖當刻，BOBO可以即時檢取你嘅電話。<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n要打電話嘅，你可以於警署，要求用警方電話打比律師，打比屋企人，叫屋企人搵律師。</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n所以我冇嘢講，係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">律師未嚟之前我冇嘢講</span></strong>，面對BOBO我冇嘢講，面對「示威者」我冇嘢講，面對家長我冇嘢講。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR<br />\n1. 「我無嘢講」係由你被捕嗰刻開始直到律師嚟之前, 對乜人 (包括手足/家長)都冇嘢講<br />\n<br />\n2. 「我無嘢講」有機會令你打贏官司冇得拎返律師費<br />\n<br />\n3. 千其唔好解鎖手機/比密碼, 用BOBO電話搵家人/律師<br />\n<br />\n4. 除非有你同意/ 搜查令, 否則無權拎你手機密碼/ 上你屋企搜屋<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果被酷刑, 要認住佢同嗰個地方個樣, 然後請律師搵當值官認人+跟進</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nCredit<br />\n「我冇嘢講」 原來有風險？被捕到底要點做？等李安然律師話你知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n李安然大律師教你被捕後面對警察的「救命招」 (文字版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc885561050bc9aa66cb4bc92de16d16cf3a165c","tid":1829318,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"f7e21f3ce1e121ebb1595590eb6ca6d0580bdbe7","tid":1829318,"uid":231759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"只要你唔係無人無物 你就無咁易被消失<br />\n總知記得同至少一個信得過嘅人報備<br />\n唔係同你一齊出嗰啲啊"},{"pid":"0a75b38017a178b7444362c4d4f386e22a59e7f3","tid":1829318,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:04:44.000Z","msg":"我要搵律師"},{"pid":"7cec58b3d14695f4ff479743eeba1ecb2a7746bd","tid":1829318,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:06:20.000Z","msg":"Up"}]}